                                "stop": 15.472,
                                "byte_start": 80094,
                                "byte_stop": 142056,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinions of the court in Massachusetts against the United States and in the case of City of Lafayette against Louisiana Power and Light company will each be announced by Mr. Justice Brennan."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 15.472,
